    # CIRRUS Haptic 9
    chown system system /sys/bus/i2c/drivers/cs40l26/0-0043/input/input9/calibration/redc_stored
    chown system system /sys/bus/i2c/drivers/cs40l26/0-0043/input/input9/calibration/f0_stored
